      },
      "date": "2021-01-27 23:04:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhat _would_ be a useful test case to add is to create a \"lustre/tests/racer/file_fallocate.sh\" script so that this operation is thrown into the merry party of commands clobbering each other in racer.\n\nWhile racer doesn't verify data correctness like fsx does, racer is multi-threaded while fsx is only single threaded, so there will be different kinds of interactions happening there.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
