        "subject": "LU-14287 tests: Improve sanity/150b test-case",
        "message": "LU-14287 tests: Improve sanity/150b test-case\n\nOn rare occasion when check_fallocate binary fails\nit leaves large $DIR/$tfile under the mount. On\nmultiple runs check_fallocate subsequently fails\nwith \"no space on device\".\n\nThis patch adds a 'stack_trap' on exit to remove\nfile/s created by the testcase on success or failure.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nChange-Id: I33643c0a8db88e30886d5f73df72282546dbc8f0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
